summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2007 JEEP LIBERTY. THE CONTACT STATED THAT THE DRIVER'S SEAT BELT FAILED TO LOCK. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT TAKEN TO THE DEALER. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT DIAGNOSED OR REPAIRED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS CONTACTED AT 800-992-1997 AND STATED THAT THE VEHICLE WAS NOT UNDER WARRANTY. THE CONTACT WAS ADVISED TO CALL NHTSA. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 152,000.  UPDATED 10/18/17*LJ  THE CONTACT TOOK THE CAR TO THE DEALER AND FIXED THE SEATBELT. *TR
